messages.message: Hello. Is CSV the only format to export data from the AI Hub, or is there some other format available? Some clients would like to export the answer in a PDF format. Is that possible?

But what could be very cool, depending on the use case, is that a CSV format can be imported into a fillable PDF - in this video in do it for one, but you can set it up differently and do it in batch mode https://youtu.be/gAsQGFvILi8?si=m6HY9tspV6VIWBwN (https://youtu.be/gAsQGFvILi8?si=m6HY9tspV6VIWBwN)
